            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Do not fall for the baby show thing of Mothers Pride (inside presidium campus ) it's a show they do for enrollment of kids.....If you baby is enrolled then they win even without going on stage.\n\nThe washrooms are in really bad condition ur kids health is in ur own hands....You have to call them urself and ask for each and everything.....I also enrolled for Most photogenic and paid Rs 1000 which was actually useless as their are no uploads on any website neither have they shared the pictures with the parents.....Don't really fall for the baby show trap",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
