            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It’s a really bad school . Bad teachers , absolutely unqualified , bad infrastructure and overall poor environment for the overall development of children . Also half of the positive reviews written here are done by teachers who teach at the school and were probably forced to write these fake good reviews . There is nothing “good” about this educational institution and the only thing this school stands for is the failure of the Indian education system .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
