            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I study in this school. Some teachers are extremely loving n caring whereas some are very rude.\nACs here don't work unless we complain. In events such as Annual day or any similar things only a handful of kids are always chosen for the main role and others are given the side role. And those some students are some sort of teachers child or something. The school all over is ok, but some teachers need to change their attitudes towards us, the ac problem needs to be solved.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
