          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My experience has been very bad with Presidium. My daughter had developmental delays and I had very transparently mentioned those to admission incharge. She claimed that school has infrastructure and we can take care of kids with development issues. However for my daughter they simply handed over my daughter to school maids as she was not going to class. They have communication gaps within the school staff/teachers and as a result kid and parents suffer.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
